videos.headline: Liberty strikes first on diving TD run
videos.description: Liberty running back Frankie Hickson bounces to the outside and dives for the goal line to score a 6-yard touchdown  vs. Idaho State.

videos.headline: Calvert airs out 29-yard TD pass for Liberty
videos.description: Stephen Calvert throws to Antonio Gandy-Golden in the end zone and he hauls it in for a 29-yard score vs. Idaho State.

videos.headline: Long Idaho State run sets up short TD pass
videos.description: Idaho State's Ty Flanagan runs up the middle for a 59-yard gain, setting up a 2-yard touchdown pass from Tanner Gueller to Austin Campbell.

videos.headline: Idaho St. connects on brother-to-brother TD
videos.description: Idaho State quarterback Tanner Gueller throws a 21-yard touchdown pass to his brother Mitch Gueller vs. Liberty.

videos.headline: Gueller throws across middle for Idaho State TD
videos.description: Idaho State's Tanner Gueller passes to Michael Dean over the middle and he outraces the Liberty defense to the end zone.

videos.headline: Liberty WR leaps, grab, stretches for TD
videos.description: Stephen Calvert throws to Antonio Gandy-Golden, who brings it down and stretches the ball over the goal line for a 37-yard Liberty touchdown.

videos.headline: Idaho State's Flanagan breaks free for 51-yard TD
videos.description: Idaho State running back Ty Flanagan runs for a 51-yard touchdown to cut into Liberty's lead in the third quarter.
